Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去下父亲的书房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱碰里面的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群有意思的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个长发的人好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是BIGRING司令的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士相关的书是这本…这本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 我去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿着走廊 到底右拐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这幢房子不像能藏得下机动战士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 剩下的可能性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士模拟格斗大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尔迪亚的年轻技师们齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装配机动战士和负责操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的智慧 热情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将在此碰撞出炽热的火花！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗 获胜 夺冠！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是48支队伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够如愿以偿的只有一队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是那支队伍最后胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得荣耀的桂冠呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.83,0:14:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一场就是决赛了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就一直没看见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 计划按时开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会马上前往汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一支进入决赛的队伍出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特曼校队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶者是法比·德鲁斯缇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拍对手队伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给亚瑟姆镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:15:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离决赛开始不到5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特干什么去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的机动战士又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你去哪 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决赛马上开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 这里拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们虽然在迎战 但坚持不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们拦不住敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的麻烦 但无碍大局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 趁我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 又来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援兵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰哈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯大人 情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 再等会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 设定完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝这招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里去了 高达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 拖延太久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果大会改期了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 据说维甘又来进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还是被那台白色机动战士打回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 亚瑟姆和杰哈特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天他们请假
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是菲利特麾下的联邦军设施
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把高达藏在这里可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 菲利特会保护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.30,0:21:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论遇到什么敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:22:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达被运出明日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.77,0:22:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达乌内斯总部下令
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.71,0:22:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续潜伏直至成功夺取高达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.42,0:22:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我刚才松了一口气？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.96,0:24:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业仪式 与好友的告别
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为战士的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悲剧的开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士高达AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业仪式上的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人的命运成就历史
