Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZedasR是XRounder专用机
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zedas的改进型机体
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.81,0:24:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同的驾驶者会让机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发挥出不同的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.12,0:24:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,XRounder专用机更是如此